Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:40.79,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}在時間中 持續徜徉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.51,0:22:48.41,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}為了故作平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.20,0:22:55.65,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\an2\pos(960,1065)}行為舉止的算式
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.01,0:22:59.94,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\an2\pos(960,1065)}解個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.47,0:23:07.43,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}如果這就是戀愛
